--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.3.2 (2018-06-12)
I: Correct 'command' variable names

* Version 2.3.1 (2018-05-31)
I: Correct 'command' variable names

* Version 2.3.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 2.2.1 (2018-04-24)
I: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 2.2.0 (2018-04-04)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.3
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.2

* Version 2.1.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
I: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.2.1 (2017-12-08)
I: Ensure role works in check mode
I: Avoid usage of raw module
I: Improve regular expression of grep command

* Version 1.2.0 (2017-10-18)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.2
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.1

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
I: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.10.0 (2017-04-16)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.1
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.0

* Version 0.9.1 (2016-12-14)
I: Consolidate and improve redundant Ansible tasks

* Version 0.9.0 (2016-10-14)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.8.0 (2016-09-03)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 6.0
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.7.2 (2016-05-29)
I: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.7.1 (2016-05-27)
I: Improve packaging tasks

* Version 0.7.0 (2016-05-21)
F: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.6.1 (2016-04-15)
I: Improve 'all' 'group' and 'host' options

* Version 0.6.0 (2016-04-09)
F: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
F: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-04-02)
F: Add support for OpenBSD 5.9
F: Drop support for OpenBSD 5.8

* Version 0.4.1 (2016-03-30)
B: Fix path parameter in remove task

* Version 0.4.0 (2016-02-29)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.3.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.2.2 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.2.1 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.2.0 (2015-05-28)
F: Update configuration file 'monitrc'

* Version 0.1.0 (2015-02-25)
F: Initial release
